{"tid":405170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（好辛苦）冇咩朋友既你失戀會點做？","createTime":"2017-09-18T15:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T07:15:33.000Z","uid":76951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2be08e02111f87c80dff094267c613cdcee7afa3","tid":405170,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"好唔開心，自己一個喊，喊完係好少少<br />\n但身邊冇人安慰自己，世界又好似變返得我自己一個咁<br />\n唉，內心果種痛，人係為咩而生，點解咁唔開心，死亡係咩？一切既虛無？無開心亦無唔開心？人係為咩而生"},{"pid":"435bec4bd00c9ba0395d62c310a604a977bd34f4","tid":405170,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"咁樣好易諗唔開"},{"pid":"2ebc4916e6b9115727c6f76541fc51939f91e915","tid":405170,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"就算有朋友<br />\n但人地唔明都係冇用"},{"pid":"c60ea55a188e5ae51fb08fe397df9a5b9fe128fd","tid":405170,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"至少搵一個人陪你<br />\n<br />\n唔好一個人面對分手"},{"pid":"b2a2c132bba9ed4ef767d0455d5daa140b903c68","tid":405170,"uid":136049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"睇書     千期唔好聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8322cb580534d5174d0687ea777d3d1cebc6433","tid":405170,"uid":54878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:11:36.000Z","msg":"出街漫無目的咁行，留意身邊發生嘅事物，你就會覺得其實世界很大"},{"pid":"5c62e48f1f8d5c9709110e20103ac61bba837bae","tid":405170,"uid":50647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"我係音樂治療架<br />\n你平時有咩喜好？<br />\n我會睇戲睇書睇綜藝Distract自己<br />\n唔好諗埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩分開係最難過架<br />\n<br />\n揮別錯的才能和對的相逢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492fb389881e34071e3804a5f1e58d94f07aaf43","tid":405170,"uid":31007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re