/> 返到黎一樣諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人叫我走，但我對上幾次旅行都同佢一齊去，一個人我個諗得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我去過一次都係失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  遲下去多2次希望可以"},{"pid":"cfc07d46ca2a854ca38f394693f46f5161613377","tid":405170,"uid":62050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"自己一個好難喊得出 最多坐係度呆<br />\n最多每幾個月無啦啦喊一次<br />\n揸緊車喊 坐係屋企喊 唱k喊<br />\n我覺得喊係好撚弱既事"},{"pid":"edfd637f23b16697976c3bdf776fc92eb92f0cef","tid":405170,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"就算有朋友都開解得唔多<br />\n試下自己搭巴士慢慢盪<br />\n行下海旁<br />\n總之就唔好自己一個屈係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}